  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IContainerFactory<BEAN>
    ContainerFactory interface class that define methods to facilitate the creation of Containers from a list of objects using different algorithms.
    IShortcutBeanContainer
    An interface to define the method of ShortcutBeanContainer and related.
